name: Pepecola
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
What is the project about?
The project is about a memecoin called PepeCola, created by the Dogecola team.

What makes your project unique?
The combination of cola marketing and cryptocurrency ownership makes the project unique.

History of your project.
The team previously launched Dogecola and is now capturing the spotlight with PepeCola due to Pepe's strong presence.

What’s next for your project?
We plan to do several listings and to become a top memecoin along being a soft drink on the market

What can your token be used for?
The token can be used for cryptocurrency investment and potentially as a means of payment or reward within the PepeCola community.
